WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.406 --> 00:00:01.263
Good morning, family!

00:00:01.263 --> 00:00:03.560
I'm excited to be with you all again today.

00:00:03.800 --> 00:00:08.206
I have a word, and I was praying about what I should talk about today.

00:00:08.400 --> 00:00:11.620
Asking the Father, I said, 'Which way do you want me to go?

00:00:11.620 --> 00:00:12.431
Which direction?

00:00:12.431 --> 00:00:37.399
' I can go a whole bunch of different directions, but in this case, I feel the Lord is wanting this for somebody; it's important for someone.

00:00:37.399 --> 00:00:47.095
Being an intercessor and a prayer person, I pray a lot.

00:00:47.095 --> 00:01:00.029
I pray, and the Lord will reveal and download things to me all the time.

00:01:00.029 --> 00:01:06.263
People say, 'How do I get there?

00:01:06.263 --> 00:01:09.102
' It's day-to-day.

00:01:21.026 --> 00:01:21.439
You do it like anything else—you're going to keep going at it.

00:01:21.896 --> 00:01:34.811
You pray, you fast, you read your Bible, and you seek His face.

00:01:34.811 --> 00:01:45.491
Whenever you seek Him, the Bible says you'll find Him.

00:01:45.491 --> 00:01:52.840
If you knock, the door will be opened.

00:01:52.840 --> 00:02:05.707
I'm telling you, He's respecter of persons, and what He'll do for one, He'll do for another.

00:02:05.707 --> 00:02:15.493
I had been dealing with a lot of satanic attacks from this YouTube channel.

00:02:15.493 --> 00:02:24.795
He's trying to stop it; he doesn't want me doing this.

00:02:24.795 --> 00:02:38.680
With all kinds of stuff from the occult, you can just feel it in the atmosphere.

00:02:38.680 --> 00:02:49.010
When you get sensitive to things and start maturing with the Lord, you're able to identify atmospheres, what's going on in the spirit realm for that day, and what's coming against you.

00:02:53.269 --> 00:03:25.266
I try not to reveal too much because they're a bunch of chickens and losers; we don't give the devil any credit, but there are things we need to talk about so that people know how to combat it.

00:03:30.730 --> 00:03:39.533
The church doesn't talk about it because they're a bunch of sugar-coated Frosted Flakes.

00:03:49.289 --> 00:04:17.620
They give you just enough to keep you alive, but it's not making you strong or able to eat the meat and know how to fight the devil off and be victorious in your Christian life.

00:04:20.520 --> 00:04:31.693
They give you the bread of affliction, just enough to crawl spiritually.

00:04:31.693 --> 00:04:52.639
Pastors, shame on you for not teaching people how to live by faith, how to stand on the Word, and how to win victoriously.

00:04:54.594 --> 00:05:05.186
I had been dealing with that occultic stuff and was praying and seeking Him, pushing back stuff.

00:05:06.364 --> 00:05:18.039
I was asking questions about what was going on, and I wasn't expecting this at all.

00:05:18.039 --> 00:05:30.733
All of a sudden, I was in my garage and an angel came before me.

00:05:30.733 --> 00:05:49.101
I was interceding for a certain minister because the Lord had put me on an assignment.

00:05:49.101 --> 00:05:58.160
This angel comes to me in a vision.

00:05:58.160 --> 00:06:15.639
I'm not saying I'm able to touch this angel like physically flesh, but I'm able to see it in the spirit realm.

00:06:15.639 --> 00:06:27.759
It was dressed similarly to how Gabriel is dressed—very much like a messenger.

00:06:27.759 --> 00:06:51.910
Warrior angels are really muscular and have armor on, but these angels have robes and gowns and are always really tall.

00:06:51.910 --> 00:06:56.275
They're tall and slender, not bulky.

00:06:56.275 --> 00:07:02.039
They look like beanpole people—really skinny and tall.

00:07:14.595 --> 00:07:14.910
This angel came to me like that.

00:07:14.910 --> 00:07:26.546
They don't have a gender; I'm trying my best to describe it.

00:07:34.394 --> 00:07:46.305
The hair is always curlier, and they have a band around their head like olive branches.

00:07:53.129 --> 00:07:58.773
He said to me, 'I've come with a message for you.

00:08:11.160 --> 00:08:13.730
The Lord has told me that Deuteronomy 28:10 was going to become real to you.

00:08:13.730 --> 00:08:20.493
' He said it was going to become Rhema to you.

00:08:20.493 --> 00:08:27.360
In these last days, that verse is going to come alive inside of you, and you are going to have an umbrella of protection—a hedge over you.

00:08:36.613 --> 00:08:36.826
He told me to cheer up and not be afraid.

00:08:47.560 --> 00:08:55.858
He said, 'The Lord has instructed me to tell you Deuteronomy is going to come alive inside of you.

00:08:55.858 --> 00:09:08.368
' He said a supernatural covering is over you, your children, and your wife.

00:09:09.506 --> 00:09:42.150
He told me to tell that other minister you're interceding for that the scripture in Deuteronomy is going to come alive on them for the occult and the persecution they're receiving.

00:09:42.150 --> 00:09:58.500
There's a supernatural push that's coming alive, like God was breathing on that verse even more concerning you.

00:09:59.385 --> 00:10:03.388
It's going to be a hedge around you.

00:10:03.388 --> 00:10:09.079
I just started worshiping the Lord.

00:10:09.079 --> 00:10:13.480
I needed that word.

00:10:13.480 --> 00:10:35.251
When the storm's going on around you, you don't whine or be mealy-mouthed because out of the abundance of the heart, the mouth speaks.

00:10:35.251 --> 00:10:49.693
If you think like a victim, the devil comes to try to kill, steal, and destroy.

00:10:53.560 --> 00:11:00.265
He is like a roaring lion seeking whom he may devour.

00:11:00.265 --> 00:11:14.888
He's coming to try to put out that flame because he doesn't like fire.

00:11:14.888 --> 00:11:26.060
Every time I go through something, the Lord says, 'Remember your training, soldier.

00:11:32.200 --> 00:11:32.620
Remember to stand upright.

00:11:34.411 --> 00:11:38.440
Don't let the enemy knock you down.

00:11:38.440 --> 00:11:46.689
You've got to get that Word down inside of you.

00:11:46.689 --> 00:12:05.937
' You can pray all you want, but it is the Word that defeats the devil.

00:12:05.937 --> 00:12:09.760
James says to submit yourself therefore unto God, resist the devil, and he will flee from you.

00:12:09.760 --> 00:12:14.545
But you've got to submit.

00:12:14.545 --> 00:12:30.022
You've got to get that Word down inside of your spirit; that is your sword.

00:12:30.022 --> 00:12:41.835
It comes out of your mouth and is able to cut the devil up.

00:12:41.835 --> 00:13:09.195
Praying is communication with the Father and maneuvering the angels, but there are times when you're dealing with the demonic where you must be binding, loosing, and pleading the blood.

00:13:14.129 --> 00:13:25.200
The Word of the Lord is what gives you power in the spiritual realm.

00:13:31.725 --> 00:13:49.079
When Jesus was baptized in the River Jordan, the Holy Spirit ascended on Him like a dove, and a voice out of heaven spoke: 'This is my Son, in whom I am well pleased.

00:13:49.079 --> 00:13:52.813
' I'm sure Lucifer heard it.

00:13:52.813 --> 00:14:10.610
Then the devil comes when Jesus is being tempted for forty days and tries to talk to Him: 'If you are the Son of God...

00:14:10.610 --> 00:14:14.051
' He started questioning it.

00:14:14.051 --> 00:14:23.851
He's a flesh devil; he doesn't think right.

00:14:28.340 --> 00:14:28.755
He has Alzheimer's or something.

00:14:28.755 --> 00:14:39.655
Jesus didn't combat him with natural things; He combated him with the Word.

00:14:49.276 --> 00:14:51.231
He said, 'It is written, Satan, tempt not the Lord thy God.

00:14:51.231 --> 00:15:02.040
' Every time He spoke back to the devil, He quoted scripture.

00:15:02.040 --> 00:15:09.383
He told the devil, 'Get thee behind me, Satan.

00:15:09.383 --> 00:15:15.893
' That's what you have to do.

00:15:15.893 --> 00:15:36.080
Every time I deal with manifestations of critters trying to come against me, I've noticed that worship ticks them off.

00:15:39.360 --> 00:15:44.794
You can make them shut up when you start worshiping.

00:15:44.794 --> 00:15:54.589
I start praising the Lord, and they get out of here.

00:16:10.820 --> 00:16:11.095
I start quoting scripture, and the devil will flee from you in terror.

00:16:18.634 --> 00:16:23.960
The Lord has done everything He's going to do about the devil for you.

00:16:23.960 --> 00:16:40.200
Ephesians says we're seated with Him in the heavenlies, far above all principalities and powers.

00:16:40.200 --> 00:16:41.310
We take dominion and authority.

00:16:46.780 --> 00:16:47.680
You use Deuteronomy; that verse is for every believer.

00:16:49.653 --> 00:17:04.538
The devil recognizes authority just like a policeman standing at a traffic sign holding up his badge.

00:17:04.538 --> 00:17:17.620
By himself, he's just another average Joe, but he has the city and state backing him.

00:17:17.620 --> 00:17:27.410
He has that badge, and you obey because you recognize the authority.

00:17:29.240 --> 00:17:42.796
The devil recognizes if you know your authority in Christ and have that badge of the Holy Ghost.

00:17:42.796 --> 00:17:48.467
The blood of Jesus is your badge.

00:17:49.977 --> 00:17:57.770
You say, 'The blood of Jesus is against you, devil.

00:17:59.069 --> 00:18:03.066
You can't touch my house or my children.

00:18:03.066 --> 00:18:11.059
I command you to let my finances go right now!

00:18:11.059 --> 00:18:25.640
' I am a joint-heir with Jesus Christ, and I tell you, 'Thus far and no further!

00:18:25.640 --> 00:18:36.667
' I hold the blood—that's my badge—and I hold the blood of Jesus over this.

00:18:36.667 --> 00:18:45.151
If you start doing that, the devil's going to flee from you.

00:18:45.151 --> 00:18:57.660
He'll come back and test if you still have a revelation of it, but if you hit him with that Holy Ghost sword, he'll go mess with somebody else who doesn't know the Word.

00:18:57.660 --> 00:19:09.320
Get the Word down inside of your spirit, and it will change your life.

00:19:09.320 --> 00:19:22.131
It is life to those that find it and health to all their flesh.

00:19:34.460 --> 00:19:40.840
2024 is going to be a year we go higher in the spirit realm, higher financially, and higher in your job.

00:19:54.549 --> 00:19:56.311
Today is your day of victory.

00:20:02.039 --> 00:20:04.749
Father, I thank you for every single believer here.

00:20:10.593 --> 00:20:25.449
I call for supernatural breakthrough for their finances and for marriages to be restored and full of freshness.

00:20:39.760 --> 00:20:45.017
Perfect love casts out all fear, but love takes no account of a suffered wrong.

00:20:45.634 --> 00:20:49.280
I thank you for the love that flows through these marriages.

00:20:49.280 --> 00:21:00.360
Today could be a brand-new start for you and your spouse.

00:21:13.329 --> 00:21:13.538
I pray blessings and increase over you in Jesus' name.

00:21:13.538 --> 00:21:34.782
Through these holiday struggles, I thank you, Father, that you give them peace and joy because Jesus is the reason for the season.

00:21:34.782 --> 00:21:47.419
He was born in a manger just for you because He loves you.

00:22:02.747 --> 00:22:08.240
I bless you all in Jesus' name.

00:22:08.240 --> 00:22:20.780
Please click that notification button, like my videos, and leave some kind comments.

00:22:20.780 --> 00:22:29.826
It helps us get the Gospel out throughout the world.

00:22:29.826 --> 00:22:39.667
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:22:44.240 --> 00:22:45.533
Jesus loves you, and we love you.

00:22:46.893 --> 00:22:50.239
We will see you next time.

00:22:50.239 --> 00:22:55.736
Have a blessed day y'all!

00:22:55.736 --> 00:22:56.776
Bye-bye.
